description.narrative: UNICEF worked in collaboration with UNDSS and the Security Cell to achieve results and reviewed all Area SRM documents and facilitated implementation of SRM-Measures at each field office (FO). After the effects of the Pandemic of 2020, the Security Team re-calibrated the 2021 Security Plan to focus on enabling programme implementation, and on implementing a capacity building training programme for national security staff to empower them at FO level. UNICEF Operations, Programme and Security teams all worked seamlessly with the UNAMI/UNDSS, and UNCT to manage risks to staff and programme delivery. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:16/01/2022
